2026-05-17T00:20:36.1957582Z 246            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1958368Z 247            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1959163Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1959963Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1960656Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1961394Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1962404Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1963485Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1964269Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-17T00:20:36.1964928Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
