2026-05-17T00:20:36.5682630Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-17T00:20:36.5682935Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-17T00:20:36.5683244Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-17T00:20:36.5683706Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-17T00:20:36.5684011Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-17T00:20:36.5684277Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
